title: The Big O (Jazmine Sullivan Interview)
itunes:title: The Big O (Jazmine Sullivan Interview)
description:
Today on the show we had Jazmine Sullivan call in and had a very insigtful and interesting conversation about relationships, what promiscuous really means, and Dj Envy's skills in the bedroom. In fact, after DJ Envy revealed he couldn't make his wife have a orgasm for several years, we made it into our Freak Friday topic. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Noah Cyrus after her comments of defending a friend turned into racist comments instead.
